<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a365d 0%, #2d3748 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        .success-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            color: #2d3748;
        }
        
        .success-icon {
            font-size: 4em;
            color: #48bb78;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .success-title {
            font-size: 2em;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #2d3748;
        }
        
        .success-message {
            color: #718096;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .purchase-details {
            background: #f7fafc;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        
        .detail-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .detail-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        
        .btn {
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin: 5px;
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background: #4299e1;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-success {
            background: #48bb78;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="success-card">
        <div class="success-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="success-title">¡Compra Exitosa!</h1>
        
        <p class="success-message">
            Tu compra se ha procesado correctamente. Ya puedes disfrutar de tu contenido.
        </p>
        
        <div class="purchase-details">
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span>Película:</span>
                <strong><%= purchase.movie_title %></strong>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span>Monto:</span>
                <strong>€<%= parseFloat(purchase.amount).toFixed(2) %></strong>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span>Método de pago:</span>
                <strong><%= purchase.payment_method %></strong>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span>Fecha:</span>
                <strong><%= new Date(purchase.created_at).toLocaleDateString('es-ES') %></strong>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-item">
                <span>Estado:</span>
                <strong style="color: #48bb78;">Completado</strong>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div style="margin-top: 25px;">
            <a href="/movie/<%= purchase.movie_id %>" class="btn btn-primary">
                <i class="fas fa-play"></i> Ver Película
            </a>
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-success">
                <i class="fas fa-home"></i> Ir al Inicio
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <div style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 0.9em; color: #718096;">
            <p>Se ha enviado un correo de confirmación a tu email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>